text: Kuryatmasovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Alginsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 259 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 39 km from Davlekanovo, 7 km from Alga. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kuryatmasovo
